2026-05-06T14:11:24.571Z [+1924.40s] 🖥️ [/__saveUserData] DB3 updated, merged 515 games {"profile":"ActionDeka","fields":{"Name":"Action Deka","Genre":"Lightgun Shooter, Beat'em Up","Arcade Platform":"Konami PC Based","Interface":"Light Gun, Steering Wheel","Tags":"motion control, action game, light gun, beat ’em up, punching, shooting, physical gameplay, Konami, multifunction controller, interactive, 2008, arcade shooter, punching and throwing, driving actions","YouTube Link":"https://www.youtube.com/results?search_query=Action+Deka+arcade+trailer","Description":"Action Deka is a motion‑controlled action game by Konami that blends light‑gun shooting with beat ’em up mechanics. Using a multifunction action controller, players mimic shooting, punching, throwing and even driving actions. Push the controller forward like a gun to blast enemies, or shake it to unleash quick jabs and hooks; other motions simulate tossing objects or steering vehicles. The game challenges you to physically act out attacks, making it a unique fusion of arcade shooting and brawling."}}

