2026-05-08T00:28:14.152Z [+3566.71s] 🖥️ [/__saveUserData] DB3 updated, merged 518 games {"profile":"OCCPinball","fields":{"Name":"Orange County Choppers","Developer":"Incredible Technologies","Publisher":"Incredible Technologies","Players":"1","Genre":"Pinball","Arcade Platform":"IT Nighthawk","Interface":"Joystick","Tags":"","YouTube Link":"","Description":"Orange County Choppers is an arcade pinball game developed by Incredible Technologies, based on the hit TV show American Chopper. The playfield captures the iconic workshop atmosphere, featuring signature visuals and sounds (bikes like the Black Widow or Jet Bike, voice clips from Paul Sr. and Paul Jr.). The gameplay stays true to classic pinball mechanics, but the themed details and ambiance immerse players in the show's competitive, family-driven spirit.","Metadata From":"Screenscraper.fr"}}
2026-05-08T00:43:21.126Z [+4473.69s] 🖥️ [/__saveUserData] DB3 updated, merged 518 games {"profile":"PowerPuttLive2012","fields":{"Name":"Power Putt Live 2012","Developer":"Incredible Technologies","Publisher":"Incredible Technologies","Players":"1-4","Genre":"Sports, Golf","Arcade Platform":"IT Nighthawk","Interface":"Trackball","Tags":"","YouTube Link":"","Description":"Across postcard-like settings, each mini-golf hole turns into a small problem to solve, where reading slopes and planning rebounds matters as much as touch and nerve. The goal is simple, but the best scores come from clever lines, controlled power and learning how the course wants the ball to move.","Metadata From":"Screenscraper.fr"}}
2026-05-08T00:43:33.128Z [+4485.69s] 🖥️ [/__saveUserData] DB3 updated, merged 518 games {"profile":"PowerPuttLive2013","fields":{"Name":"Power Putt Live 2013","Developer":"Incredible Technologies","Publisher":"Incredible Technologies","Players":"1-4","Genre":"Sports, Golf","Arcade Platform":"IT Nighthawk","Interface":"Trackball","Tags":"","YouTube Link":"","Description":"Every hole is a bite-sized puzzle of slopes, rebounds and risk management, where a safe line can be smart but a bold bank shot can win the round. The 2013 edition greatly expands the tour with five new 18-hole courses, bringing the total to eleven, and leans harder into arcade progression by unlocking new outfits and achievement badges through play. A new Poker Putt mode reshuffles what “a good hole” means, while LIVE connectivity adds stat tracking and daily contests; for adult venues, an optional RawTalk commentary setting can be enabled.","Metadata From":"Screenscraper.fr"}}
2026-05-08T00:43:44.378Z [+4496.94s] 🖥️ [/__saveUserData] DB3 updated, merged 518 games {"profile":"SilverStrikeBowlingLive","fields":{"Name":"Silver Strike Bowling Live","Developer":"Incredible Technologies","Publisher":"Incredible Technologies","Players":"1-8","Genre":"Sports, Bowling","Arcade Platform":"IT Nighthawk","Interface":"Trackball","Tags":"","YouTube Link":"","Description":"In a world where bowling becomes a national competition, players embody virtual bowlers in realistic alleys inspired by the best bowling centers. Each game is an opportunity to prove their precision, strategy, and consistency, with pins reacting just like in real life. Online tournaments allow players to challenge opponents worldwide, while special modes like 'Spare Challenge' or 'Vegas Mode' (where every strike or spare deals a playing card) add an element of chance and fun.","Metadata From":"Screenscraper.fr"}}
2026-05-08T00:44:02.444Z [+4515.00s] 🖥️ [/__saveUserData] DB3 updated, merged 518 games {"profile":"TargetTossProBags","fields":{"Name":"Target Toss Pro Bags","Developer":"Incredible Technologies","Publisher":"Incredible Technologies","Players":"1-4","Genre":"Sports, Shuffleboard","Arcade Platform":"IT Nighthawk","Interface":"Trackball","Tags":"","YouTube Link":"","Description":"The popular American backyard game of beanbag toss (or cornhole) comes to life in this accessible arcade experience. Players take turns tossing bags toward a raised platform with a hole, aiming to score points by landing on the board or—even better—sinking the bag into the hole. The game faithfully recreates the rules and competitive spirit of real-life tournaments, with simple yet effective graphics and intuitive controls via trackball or controller. The arcade version also includes variations, like giant lawn darts, to spice up the gameplay.","Metadata From":"Screenscraper.fr"}}
2026-05-08T00:44:14.978Z [+4527.54s] 🖥️ [/__saveUserData] DB3 updated, merged 518 games {"profile":"TargetTossProLawndarts","fields":{"Name":"Target Toss Pro Lawn Darts","Developer":"Incredible Technologies","Publisher":"Incredible Technologies","Players":"1-4","Genre":"Sports, Shuffleboard","Arcade Platform":"IT Nighthawk","Interface":"Trackball","Tags":"","YouTube Link":"","Description":"A controversial backyard game makes a comeback in arcade form: players throw giant lawn darts at a ground target, aiming for the center to score the most points. Four game modes are available, including classic 'Lawn Darts,' '501' (inspired by pub darts), 'Cricket,' and 'Poker Darts,' each with unique rules and strategies.","Metadata From":"Screenscraper.fr"}}
